text: Kompany is a surname. It may refer to: *François Kompany (born 1989), Belgian footballer of Congolese descent *Pierre Kompany (born 1947), Belgian politician *Vincent Kompany (born 1986), Belgian footballer of Congolese descent It may also refer to: * Kompany (musician), an American electronic dance music producer ==See also== *"Kompanie" (2018 song) rap song by Bonez MC and RAF Camora, from the album Palmen aus Plastik 2 *Electric Kompany, American band *L-KO Kompany, an American motion picture company founded by Henry Lehrman that produced silent comedy shorts between 1914 and 1919 *Company (disambiguation)
title: Kompany (disambiguation)
